Certain of Blackstone&#8217;s consolidated real estate funds guarantee payments to third parties in connection with the ongoing business activities and/or acquisitions of their Portfolio Companies. There is no direct recourse to Blackstone to fulfill such obligations. To the extent that underlying funds are required to fulfill guarantee obligations, Blackstone&#8217;s invested capital in such funds is at risk. Total investments at risk in respect of guarantees extended by consolidated real estate funds was $ 18.3 million as of December 31, 2022. 

